channel.title: Help with the Silab client thing?
channel.description: I need help downloading that client for all those new stuff. What do I do after i click on the download part its on winrar but I need help unpacking it and stuff.

item.title: Help with the Silab client thing?
item.dc:creator: @Runer_King Runer King
item.description:
@Runer_King wrote:

Once downloaded winrar should open…Highlight all the files, then right click. It should say (about 4-6 lines down) extract to a specified folder…Click that. Then another window opens, on the top of the list, it should say desktop…click that, then click “ok” or “extract” idk, which ever is there.

item.title: Help with the Silab client thing?
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

When you open it with winrar click
Extract to > OK
The .rar archive will be extracted into a new folder where-ever you downloaded the silab client.
